    "question_id" : 8367312,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>The problem may be because you have declared variable as <code>private</code>.\nIf you change it to <code>public</code>, it works.</p>\n\n<p>Better option is to use getter and setter methods for it.</p>\n\n<p>This will solve the issue!</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 210642,
      "reputation" : 8904,
      "user_id" : 1347816,
